Okay, so first things off @Lori, I will try and give you a quick rundown
There are 3 statuses in this game for each role
Alignment (wolf or village)
Killing (can kill or cannot kill)
Witchcraft (has magic or doesn't have magic)
The tarot cards that the Arcanist sees represent these statutes
statuses*
Alignment - Hound (is a wolf), Dove (is village)
Killing - Death (can kill), Dove (cannot kill)
Witchcraft - Magician (has magic), Labourer (no magic)
As you can see, Dove can stand for two things, as an alignment card it means village, as a killing card it means cannot kill
The Arcanist can choose to compare two people and see where their cards differ
